  "title": "阶跃首席科学家张祥雨合著论文 ResNet 获 CVPR 2026 「时间检验奖」",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNTYxNzg5Mg==&mid=2247487873&idx=1&sn=48534d3e883573c603a58e114cbe8709",
